lead_paragraph: Aaron Finch is to be dumped as Australia's captain in the shortest form of the game and replaced by test skipper Steve Smith just a month before the start of the World Twenty20, The Age newspaper reported on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Finch Dumped as Australia T20 Skipper-Report
